\section{Systems supported}{

Automatically adapts column detection to SINAN, SIM, SIH, CNES, SIA, and
SINASC. Run \code{sus_data_create_variables()} before this function to generate
\code{age_group}, \code{year}, \code{month}, \code{epidemiological_week}, and
\code{climate_risk_group}.
